CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 22, 1969, pg. 11, reads: "Group Celebrates 75th Anniversary With Dinner - The Aurora Reading Club recently celebrated its Diamond Jubilee with a dinner party in the Monongahela Room of the William Penn Hotel.  The members of one of the oldest clubs in Pittsburgh, are pictured with their guest speaker (front row center), Mrs. Vivian Davidson Hewitt of New York City."
TitMainTitle: Members of Aurora Club, including Vivian Davidson Hewitt fifth from left in front, Maudelena Johnson eigth from left, and Wilhelmina Byrd Brown seventh from left in rear, posed in Monongahela Room of William Penn Hotel for anniversary dinner
